    <description>An intelligent less-lethal sniper rifle with integrated biometric tracking. Projectiles load nanoscale electroshock fibers and sedative aerosol, deploying nine guidance filaments through rifling-induced spin. Induces neuronal hyperpolarization within 3 seconds of impact for precise 15-minute paralysis. Recoil mitigation system enables surgical non-lethal interventions at 1.2km range.\n\nDesigned for spec-ops policing, this weapon can penetrate bulletproof glass while maintaining non-lethal efficacy. Its signature spiral etchings - nine helical grooves radiating from impact points - serve as forensic markers.</description>
